snippet.textDisplay: Congratulations to the entire team! Beautifully done. Xulfi has been doing an excellent job of promoting fresh talent; starting with Nescafe basement and now Coke Studio. We've already seen so many new faces this season, but one of the most talented musicians I've come across in recent years from Pakistan has been the co-producer Abdullah Siddiqui. He is only 20 yrs old and has already produced such amazingly good music. Check him out if your haven't already!
snippet.textOriginal: Congratulations to the entire team! Beautifully done. Xulfi has been doing an excellent job of promoting fresh talent; starting with Nescafe basement and now Coke Studio. We've already seen so many new faces this season, but one of the most talented musicians I've come across in recent years from Pakistan has been the co-producer Abdullah Siddiqui. He is only 20 yrs old and has already produced such amazingly good music. Check him out if your haven't already!
